column5: Here's some pictures of our trip to quinte ! All the fish were caught on weedlines using cranks !
nice going I love fishing quinte
Nice shooting!  I love fishing that body of water.
nice bunch of eyes there . If only TO weren't in the way, I would be there a lot more.
Great fish !! Quinte is on my Bucket list for this year!!!
Great fish, great t-shirt!  Looks like you had a memorable trip.  Thanks for the report
Some really nice Quinte gold. I agree with Rick, though, TO is a royal pain.  Can't we just build a giant bridge over it
This trip will be the last one for the wife and me for a while as my wife is 61/2 months pregnant with are boy !
Nice fish....and your personal best to come in a couple of months!
nice solid fish, looked like you had a great time
Looks like you guys had an awsome time!  A good last trip out for your wife!  Tis the season, seems to be lots of people having babies this fall! (myself included)
